I will cover the different field categories gradually throughout this
book. For now, the most important fields are [[id]] (a unique integer
identifying the window, visible through [[/mnt/wsys/winid]]) and
[[name]] (used by the graphics layer to find the window's image
via [[namedimage]], visible through [[/mnt/wsys/winname]]).

