%claude:
A mouse event is forwarded to the window when: the cursor is inside
the window and either it is a left-click (used for text selection in
textual windows), or [[mouseopen]] is set (meaning the application
opened [[/mnt/wsys/mouse]] and wants raw mouse events), or automatic
scrolling is active.
