\subsection{Mouse events listening}

%yoann: introduce second part
%claude:
The second connection is the mouse. Each window embeds a full
[[Mousectl]] structure whose [[c]] channel receives mouse events
from [<mousethread()>].  This is not the same [[Mousectl]] as the
one used by [[rio]]'s own IO proc for reading [[/dev/mouse]]---that
