\subsection{[[/mnt/wsys/kdbin]]}

%claude:
The [[/mnt/wsys/kdbin]] file is write-only and restricted to the
keyboard window. Writing to it converts the bytes to runes and
injects them into the keyboard channel, making them appear as
if the user had typed them on a real keyboard.

